::Ender::
       He grumbles and picks up his datapad again.  "Our two closest 
neighbors are the Destrons and the Alliance.  They also happen to be the two 
we will most easily get along with.  By that I mean our interests are often 
similar.  We are already allied with the Destrons so I suggest contacting 
Zardus of the Alliance."

--part1_d8.a506454.28a87b56_boundary
